OL,3,CIceland supermarket could employ
OL,4,Ccriminals to help them avoid jail
OL,6,FIceland Foods could employ criminals
OL,7,Fat its supermarkets instead of them
OL,8,Ffacing prison time, bosses have said.
OL,10,FThe concept could see low-risk
OL,11,Foffenders handed a suspended sentence
OL,12,Fand given a role at the company
OL,13,Finstead of being jailed.
