OL,3,CIceland supermarket could employ
OL,4,Ccriminals to help them avoid jail
OL,6,FPaul Cowley, Iceland's first director
OL,7,Fof rehabilitation, told The Times
OL,8,FCrime and Justice Commission: "If it
OL,9,Fall goes well, then that's your
OL,10,Fsentence. You don't go to prison. You
OL,11,Fdon't lose your home, kids don't go
OL,12,Finto care. And if it doesn't, and it
OL,13,Fall goes pear shaped, then it's a
OL,14,Fsuspended sentence which kicks in.
OL,16,F"But it's an opportunity to get rid of
OL,17,Fa custodial sentence. And I believe,
OL,18,Fand the company believes, that that
OL,19,Fwould have some impact on reducing
OL,20,Freoffending and our prison population."
