OL,3,CIceland supermarket could employ
OL,4,Ccriminals to help them avoid jail
OL,6,FWhile the framework has yet to be
OL,7,Fapproved, Mr Cowley and Iceland CEO
OL,8,FRichard Walker have presented the idea
OL,9,Fin a letter to Prisons Minister Lord
OL,10,FTimpson to discuss tactics to ease
OL,11,Fprison overcrowding.
OL,13,FIceland has already launched the
OL,14,F'Second Chance' initiative, which has
OL,15,Fseen more than 330 ex-offenders hired
OL,16,Fas front-line retail workers and
OL,17,Fdelivery drivers as of August 2024.
OL,19,FA further 300 currently hold job
OL,20,Foffers from the company.
