OL,6,FThe blueprint set out to Lord Timpson
OL,7,Fencourages the government and other
OL,8,Fbusinesses to consider adopting
OL,9,Fsimilar measures.
OL,11,FLord Timpson, the former chief
OL,12,Fexecutive of Timpson Group, pro-
OL,13,Factively recruited ex-offenders during
OL,14,Fhis time at the helm of the family
OL,15,Fbusiness.
OL,17,FBy the time he stepped down from his
OL,18,Fpost following the last at the
OL,19,Felection, an estimated 10% of all
OL,20,FTimpson Group employees were former
OL,21,Fconvicts.
