OL,3,CIceland supermarket could employ
OL,4,Ccriminals to help them avoid jail
OL,6,FThe so-called operational capacity for
OL,7,FEnglish and Welsh men's and women's
OL,8,Fprisons is 88,822, indicating there is
OL,9,Fcell space for 2,733 criminals.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Justice has promised
OL,12,Fto find a total of 14,000 cell spaces
OL,13,Fin prisons by 2031.
OL,15,FSome 6,400 of these will be at newly
OL,16,Fbuilt prisons, with #2.3 billion
OL,17,Fpledged towards the cost over the next
OL,18,Ftwo years.
OL,20,FThe Ministry declined to comment on
OL,21,FIceland's proposal.
